RDP
  [HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Control\Terminal Server\WinStations\RDP-Tcp]
  “SecurityLayer”=dword:00000001
  “UserAuthentication”=dword:0x00000000

VNC Root Display Issue
  switch to root and merge Xauthority
  sudo -i
  xauth merge /home/user/.Xauthority
  
Chrome Choppy Text
  Load chrome://settings/ in the browser's address bar or select Menu > Settings.
  Click on "advanced" at the bottom of the page.
  Scroll down to the "system" section.
  Toggle "Use hardware acceleration when available" to off.
  Restart Google Chrome.
